videos.description: Tyler Davis fights for an offensive rebound and goes back up strong for the bucket.
videos.headline: Davis dominates offensive glass for Aggies

videos.description: Aggies' guard TJ Starks drives the lane and finds Tyler Davis under the hoop for the dunk and foul.
videos.headline: Starks drives and dishes for Davis dunk

videos.description: Texas A&M's TJ Starks throws the high lob for Robert Williams, who collects and slams it home. Collin Sexton advantageously flashes down the floor for the finish on the other end.
videos.headline: Williams and Sexton trade fast-break finishes

videos.description:
Texas A&M's Admon Gilder drains the 3-
 pointer through contact and falls, but no foul was called.
videos.headline: Aggies take lead on Gilder's triple

videos.description: Collin Sexton ties the game at 52-52 with a running floater in the lane
videos.headline: Sexton hits 20 points, ties game

videos.description: Texas A&M's Jay Jay Chandler drives and kicks to DJ Hogg in the corner for 3, giving the Aggies a 4-point lead.
videos.headline: Hogg pads Aggies' lead with corner 3

videos.description: Texas A&M's TJ Starks pushes his hand in the face of Alabama's Collin Sexton, and Starks is ejected with less than a minute left to play.
videos.headline: Starks ejected after striking Sexton

videos.description: Texas A&M junior Tyler Davis talks about his mindset heading into the game vs. the Tide and how it feels to win for the seniors.
videos.headline: Davis says Bama win 'extremely important' for momentum
